        public <R extends Service> R getService(Class<R> serviceRole)
        Description copied from interface: ServiceRegistry
        Retrieve a service by role. If service is not found, but a ServiceInitiator is registered for this service role, the service will be initialized and returned.

        NOTE: We cannot return <R extends Service<T>> here because the service might come from the parent...
